  <body>
  <div>
    <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_snomed_international">SNOMED International</xref>
 is an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_snomed_international">International Health Terminology Standards Development Organisation</xref>
 is now more commonly referred to by its trading name 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_snomed_international">SNOMED International</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_snomed_international">SNOMED International</xref>
 develops and promotes the use of 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_snomed_ct">SNOMED CT</xref>
® to support safe and effective health information exchange.        </p>
    <p>
For further information on 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_snomed_international">SNOMED International</xref>, see the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_snomed_international">SNOMED International</xref>
 website at: 
              <xref href="https://www.snomed.org/" scope="external" format="html">SNOMED International: Home</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
